OL,3,CReeves faces up to the mother of all
OL,4,Cfiscal crises
OL,6,FThat still leaves an enormous deficit,
OL,7,Feven if the Treasury were to eliminate
OL,8,Fsome of the programmes and spending it
OL,9,Fidentified as otiose when Reeves
OL,10,Finitially announced that spending was
OL,11,Fover-budget in the current year to the
OL,12,Ftune of #22 billion.
OL,14,FLittle wonder departments from
OL,15,Ftransport, to housing and transport
OL,16,Fare having kittens about the savings
OL,17,Fthey are being asked to find.
