OL,3,CReeves faces up to the mother of all
OL,4,Cfiscal crises
OL,6,FReeves's belated reworking of the debt
OL,7,Ffiscal rules would only create
OL,8,Fadditional borrowing space for much-
OL,9,Fneeded capital investment - which will
OL,10,Fbe seen as welcome - but not for day-
OL,11,Fto-day spending.
OL,13,FSo, on my rough calculations the
OL,14,Fgovernment needs to find at least #10
OL,15,Fbillion from expenditure cuts.
OL,17,FRight now I can't see how Reeves
OL,18,Fescapes measures - spending cuts -
OL,19,Fthat will look and feel a lot like the
OL,20,Fausterity Starmer swore not to re-
OL,21,Fintroduce.
